text: Palais d'York. The Palais d'York is a historic mansion in Nice, Alpes- Maritimes, France. It was built from 1762 to 1768. It has been listed as an official national monument since December 16, 1949. ==References== Category:Houses completed in 1768 Category:Monuments historiques of Nice Category:1768 establishments in France
